                 ####How would this be configured to maximize availability###

Keep docker images small so they can launch fast by using small amounts of memory.

Keep process at minimum  to save CPU  and memory usage.

Utilize orchestration to docker swarm to manage docker containers upon demand. 

                 ###What loads would this spinup be able to handle.#####
                 
                Use nginx as  a proxy to load over specific port request 
                
                #####How would logging, security be applied#####

Avoid running container with root privilege.

Keep credential in vaults with th euse of a third party application.

Use vulnerability software to scan your software for any risk. 

Utilize jfrog artifactory to store docker image away from the public. 

Implement tls certs on web server. 

Rotate database credential ever  45 days.            
                
